WEBVTT

00:07.723 --> 00:09.724
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
WITH THE CLARK BAR?

00:09.792 --> 00:11.559
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
A SNICKERS MAN.

00:11.627 --> 00:14.362
OH. I DELIVERED
TO AN ED CLARK TODAY,

00:14.430 --> 00:17.365
AND, WELL, ONE THING
LED TO ANOTHER.

00:19.301 --> 00:23.922
ANY CHANCE YOU MIGHT DELIVER
TO A STEVE CELERY SOMETIME?

00:23.989 --> 00:27.358
ANY CHANCE YOU COULD
DELIVER TO SHUTTY TOWN?

00:29.762 --> 00:31.630
I USED TO LOVE THESE
AS A KID.

00:31.697 --> 00:33.832
MMM.

00:33.900 --> 00:36.367
ACTUALLY STOLE ONE
ONCE.

00:36.435 --> 00:37.702
YOU STOLE?

00:37.770 --> 00:39.604
YEP. I WAS AT HERB'S CANDIES ONE DAY.

00:39.671 --> 00:41.639
I CAME UP
A DIME SHORT,

00:41.707 --> 00:43.641
SO I JUST PUT ONE
IN MY POCKET,

00:43.709 --> 00:45.810
SLIPPED OUT THE FRONT DOOR AND ATE IT.

00:45.878 --> 00:48.512
5 MINUTES LATER, I FELT SO
GUILTY I THREW IT ALL UP.

00:50.116 --> 00:52.650
AND YET YOU GOT BACK
ON THE HORSE.

00:55.521 --> 00:57.789
HOW ABOUT YOU, YOU EVER STEAL ANYTHING?

00:57.856 --> 00:59.824
UH... ONCE
IN HIGH SCHOOL,

00:59.892 --> 01:01.993
A BUNCH OF US
STOLE A CAR.

01:08.284 --> 01:10.519
I'M SORRY?

01:11.587 --> 01:13.505
WELL, IF YOU WANT
TO BE TECHNICAL,

01:13.573 --> 01:16.074
IT WAS MORE OF
A CARJACKING.

01:16.142 --> 01:19.244
THE, UH, THE SHOP TEACHER
MR. PESHKIN

01:19.312 --> 01:21.313
WAS GONNA FAIL
A BUNCH OF US,

01:21.380 --> 01:22.947
SO WE WAITED FOR HIM
AFTER SCHOOL, AND, UM,

01:23.015 --> 01:25.200
WHEN HE WAS CLIMBING
INTO HIS CRAPPY OLD BUICK,

01:25.267 --> 01:27.318
MY FRIEND JIMMY
CAME UP BEHIND HIM,

01:27.386 --> 01:29.320
AND HE WAS, LIKE,
"GET DOWN! GET DOWN!"

01:29.388 --> 01:31.172
LIKE HE HAD A GUN
OR SOMETHING.

01:31.323 --> 01:33.825
SO MR. PESHKIN, HE JUST
DROPPED TO THE PAVEMENT,

01:33.893 --> 01:36.627
AND WE JUST ALL PILED
IN HIS CAR AND TOOK OFF.

01:36.695 --> 01:38.213
HE NEVER SAW US.

01:38.280 --> 01:40.147
BUT THEN LATER ON, WE STARTED
FREAKING OUT ABOUT FINGERPRINTS,

01:40.216 --> 01:42.149
SO WE STRIPPED
THE LICENSE PLATES

01:42.218 --> 01:44.586
AND PUSHED THE CAR
INTO THE RIVER.

01:44.653 --> 01:48.556
IT'S CRAZY THE STUFF
YOU DO AS A KID, RIGHT?

01:50.000 --> 01:56.074
